<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">In this book, patents and lawsuits are mentioned but little attention is given to the Wright&apos;s legal battles. This book mostly covers just their perio<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">In this book, patents and lawsuits are mentioned but little attention is given to the Wright's legal battles. This book mostly covers just their period of innovation from around 1900 to 1911.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
